es. Explore ways you can help prepare your organization’s workforce for generative AI. Plus, go over some important legal and ethical responsibilities and ideas on how generative AI will impact business, work, jobs, and HR processes.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>','','37','','','','','Y','status.completed','content.program','',0),(57,'',56,56,0,'N',1554,'2024-04-05 10:55:39',1554,'2024-04-05 10:55:39.408300','GENERATIVE AI IN HR',0,0,'','','growthplan.content.type.poc','https://samsungu.csod.com/ui/lms-learning-details/app/course/cfde784a-e089-507e-9429-42f837de7fbb','','','','','','','','N','status.draft','content.program.task','1 HOURS',100),(58,'',0,0,0,'N',0,'2024-04-05 11:07:44',1554,'2024-04-05 11:07:44.229539','GENERATIVE AI FOR BUSINESS LEADERS',1554,1083,'skill.level.learner','skill.level.beginner','content.course.type.skillup','','<p>DETAILS</p><p>Are you eager to do more than just scratch the surface of Generative AI for Business?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Welcome to the <strong>Generative AI for Business</strong> – a course crafted to get you familiar with Generative AI, made for tech enthusiasts, business leaders, professional workers, and simply anyone who wants to learn about Generative AI in the business landscape. Whether you\'re diving into the world of AI for the first time or seeking to elevate your business strategy, this course is designed to equip you with the skills to leverage and talk about Generative AI effectively.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>In this course, we guide you through the <strong>foundations, applications, and best practices of Generative AI, providing practical insights and real-world case studies</strong>. From understanding the benefits and drawbacks of these models to exploring their diverse applications in <strong>analytics, general use, knowledge management, and application development</strong>, this course ensures a comprehensive learning experience.</p><p><br><strong>What is Generative AI?</strong></p><p>Generative AI, a branch of machine learning and deep learning, creates new, realistic data by learning patterns. It\'s like a digital artist generating images or text. In this course, you\'ll explore how Generative AI demonstrates its practical applications in enhancing business solutions and fostering innovation. You will understand its different flavors, its benefits, its drawbacks, the future of Generative AI, and its applications in business settings.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>What is this course all about?</strong></p><p>Generative AI is pivotal in transforming industries by revolutionizing content creation, analytics, and strategic decision-making. In this course, explore its <strong>popularity, benefits, and drawbacks, and understand its real-world applications through case studies</strong>. From <strong>creating summaries to designing logos and apps</strong>, discover how Generative AI shapes the future of business innovation.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Why Choose This Course?</strong></p><p><strong>Fully Instructional</strong> - Access a comprehensive introduction to Generative AI, providing foundational knowledge for learners of all levels.</p><p><strong>Best Practices Exploration</strong> - Understand effective strategies through the exploration of best practices in Generative AI.</p><p><strong>Real-world Applications</strong> - Engage with fully instructional case studies, including creating summaries, explaining formulas, and logo and app creation.</p><p><strong>Comprehensive Learning</strong> - Delve into the transformative impact of Generative AI across various business domains, covering efficiency, creativity, analytics, and app development.</p><p><strong>All-inclusive Reference</strong> - Utilize all the reference materials used in course creation, ensuring a comprehensive learning experience.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Course Overview:</strong></p><p><strong>Introduction</strong> - Explore the foundational concepts of Generative AI and its relevance in business and access the resources, and reading materials used in the course.</p><p><strong>Understanding Generative AI for Business</strong> - Delve into the core principles and functionalities of Generative AI, investigate the widespread adoption and impact across industries, examine the practical benefits. understand the potential challenges and limitations associated with it, navigate the ethical implications surrounding the use of Generative AI, gain insights into the evolving landscape and future trends, and learn effective strategies and best practices for integrating Generative AI into business operations.</p><p><strong>Applications in Business</strong> - Explore real-world applications through diverse case studies, including app creation, analytics, and knowledge management.</p><p><strong>Case Studies Across Domains</strong> - Engage in detailed case studies covering various business scenarios, from logo creation to app development.</p>','','0','rohit.marwah','','','','Y','status.inprogress','content.program','',0),(59,'',58,58,0,'N',1554,'2024-04-05 11:07:44',1554,'2024-04-05 11:07:44.293274','GENERATIVE AI FOR BUSINESS LEADERS',0,0,'','','growthplan.content.type.poc','https://samsungu.csod.com/ui/lms-learning-details/app/onlineContent/5679161b-c450-547b-8893-7c9472d50816','','','','','','','','N','status.draft','content.program.task','2 hours',100),(60,'',0,0,0,'N',0,'2024-04-05 11:11:02',1554,'2024-04-05 11:11:01.699514','GENERATIVE AI for  Software Quality Engineering',1554,1083,'skill.level.learner','skill.level.beginner','content.course.type.skillup','','<p><strong>DETAILS (instructions on email)</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>This is a masterclass in Quality Engineering teaching the student how to properly approach quality validations by applying shift left and Right approaches, Dev Ops tool chain and Lean principles. This will provide an in dept analysis on how one can have preventive measures before the first line of code is written and how to maximize the return on the investment made in quality engineering.</p><p>The main goal of this course is to put together all the individual pieces that make software testing: Automation, Devops, Agile, Functional, Non-Functional, Version Control, Shift left and Shift Right, Containers, X as Code, Automated quality checks, Environments, Cloud and so on into one lecture that will bring these topics in a LEAN approach. This will take you from average Quality engineer to quality transformation expert.</p><p>You will see how to overcome the storming and norming phase in the team and reach the high performing state by looking at the model based on the five dysfunctions of the team.</p><p>After this lecture you will be able to improve the efficiency of your process, reduce infrastructure cost related to quality engineering, increase the speed of execution. By explaining LEAN Concepts and TIMWOODS wastes the project and organization will move to a continuous improvement and innovation state.</p>','','10,7','','','rohit.marwah','','Y','status.inprogress','content.program','',0),(61,'',60,60,0,'N',1554,'2024-04-05 11:11:04',1554,'2024-04-05 11:11:04.260845','GENERATIVE AI FOR  Software Quality Engineering',0,0,'','','growthplan.content.type.poc','https://samsungu.csod.com/ui/lms-learning-details/app/onlineContent/ce64318e-feb3-5d5f-960f-84f5e4f381b9','','','','','','','','N','status.draft','content.program.task','2 hours',100),(62,'',0,0,0,'N',0,'2024-04-05 11:39:56',1554,'2024-04-05 11:39:56.186926','GENERATIVE AI IN HR',1554,1083,'skill.level.learner','skill.level.beginner','content.course.type.skillup','','<p>From job descriptions to skills evaluation to recruiting assistance, generative AI is transforming HR departments. In this course, work futurist, consultant, speaker, and author Dr. Terri Horton guides you through transformations that are occurring and how you can use them effectively in your HR department. Learn how generative AI catalyzes, transforms, and amplifies HR in talent acquisition and onbo